title: (Mon Early) The Epic Conclusion of 2 Truths and a Lie + Travis Denning on His Wedding Date + Plays Famous Guitar Licks
itunes:title: (Mon Early) The Epic Conclusion of 2 Truths and a Lie + Travis Denning on His Wedding Date + Plays Famous Guitar Licks
description:
Our final 4 listeners face off with the chance to win the pot in 2 Truths in a Lie. They go elimination style guessing is Bobby’s stories are true or lies.

Travis Denning stops by the studio and hangs out with his guitar. He shares the first licks he ever learned to play, a song he wrote for his first punk band and when he is getting married.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
